title: Seitokaichou ga Yuri-zuki demo Mondai Nashi!?
original_name: 生徒会長が百合好きでも問題ナシ!?
sinopse: Kanon is the popular student council president at her elite private girls' school. However, she has a secret hobby that she hides from everyone except her maid Kurumi—she is an obsessive yuri fan. She also likes Kurumi, and Kurumi seems to have a secret of her own too.
